Michael Harney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Harney 0 Michael John Harney (born March 27, 1956) is an American actor of film, television, and theater. He is best known for starring on the SAG Award-winning Netflix original series Orange Is the New Black as Corrections Officer Sam Healy.
